The '''Bothan Martial Academy''', also known as the '''Bothan Military Academy''', was a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] military academy. Although often mocked, the academy produced many officers and soldiers during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] to protect the Bothans' neutrality. [[Peshk Vri'syk]], [[Asyr Sei'lar]] and [[Traest Kre'fey]] were graduates. [[Wraith Squadron]] [[Slicer/Legends|slicer]] [[Eurrsk Thri'ag]] attended the academy prior to enlisting in the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] in order to become a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]].

